@Marky8882 @adrianaNFT when you list NFTs for sale, you need to give OS (or whatever platform you are listing on) approval to move that token on your behalf

this is done on the contract level for the NFT you're selling

OS has approvals to move any token from a collection you listed, unless you revoke

@adrianaNFT disconnecting won't help

it's less of a hack and more of a massively successful phishing campaign

if you are worried about your NFTs, use https://t.co/OSKPEBor7A to revoke approvals for them

